      "narration": "A logit is useful for the model, but it is not yet a probability that we can interpret comfortably. The sigmoid fixes that by mapping any real-valued score onto the range from zero to one. A bigger positive logit would push us closer to one, a negative logit would push us toward zero, and this particular score lands at about zero point six seven six. So the network is leaning toward the positive class with moderate confidence.",
